stations de prévention des infections.</div></div><div class="flex-item-uls"><ul class="flex-item-uls-li"><li class="flex-item-uls-lis"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-flex"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-left"><span class="flex-item-uls-lis-circle"></span></div><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-right"><span>Qualité Supérieure</span></div></div></li><li class="flex-item-uls-lis"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-flex"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-left"><span class="flex-item-uls-lis-circle"></span></div><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-right"><span>Vitesse & Temps Réglables</span></div></div></li><li class="flex-item-uls-lis"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-flex"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-left"><span class="flex-item-uls-lis-circle"></span></div><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-right"><span>Fonctionnement Silencieux & Stable</span></div></div></li><li class="flex-item-uls-lis"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-flex"><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-left"><span class="flex-item-uls-lis-circle"></span></div><div class="flex-item-uls-lis-right"><span>Grande Plateforme</span></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="flex-item border-left"><p></p><script>    (function(window, document) {      var docEl = document.documentElement      var viewEl = document.querySelector('meta[name=viewport]')      var dpr = window.devicePixelRatio || 1      var scale = 1 / dpr      function layout() {        var rem = docEl.clientWidth * 100 / 750        docEl.style.fontSize = rem + 'px'      }      viewEl.setAttribute('content', 'width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,user-scalable=no')      layout()      window.addEventListener('resize', layout)      window.addEventListener('pageshow', function(e) {        if (e.presisted) {          layout()        }      })    })(window, document)  </script><div id="pc"><div class="flex-item-content"><div style="margin-top: 11px; text-align: center;"><img class="js-descLazyload " src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAD/ACwAAAAAAQABAAACAD